  "body": "### Description\r\n\r\n*Type*: Bug\r\n\r\n*Summary*: When i tap `Advanced` button anywhere it exists - i dont want to scroll the screen - the options should appear via autoscroll \r\n\r\n#### Expected behavior\r\nscreen is autoscrolled when I tap Advanced so I dont need to scroll\r\n\r\n#### Actual behavior\r\nI need to scroll the screen to reach the Advanced options. Here is the list of them:\r\n\r\n1. Home -> Profile -> advanced\r\n2. Home -> 1x1 chat (Jarrad) -> Send transaction -> advanced\r\n3. Home -> Open dapp -> Send transaction to dapp -> advanced\r\n4. Home -> Group chat - Send transaction -> advanced\r\n\r\n![image](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/28752642/37906977-79b03aa6-310c-11e8-82da-b1a5934e5f84.png)\r\n\r\n\r\n### Additional Information\r\n* Status version: nightly 26/03/2018\r\n* Operating System: Android, iOS",
